    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every weekend, and driven with nothing but love. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape; honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I noticed one tiny, barely-there stone chip on the hood that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, but other than that, she\u2019s absolutely flawless. It\u2019s smooth, reliable, and ready for a new home. Come take a look, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of something really special!",
